&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WPP Enterprise Solutions designs, builds, and operates the growth systems that competitive businesses rely on. In a world where Al is reshaping how companies drive growth, we lead clients in business transformation and marketing modernization, connecting strategy directly to execution. Our 12,000 experts in engineering and platforms, commerce, consulting, content transformation, CRM, and CX work within a unified global operating unit across 40+ markets. WPP Enterprise Solutions works alongside best-in-class partners including Adobe, AWS, Braze, Google, Microsoft, Salesforce, and Shopify, as well as innovators in AI, to deliver growth solutions tailored to the needs of our clients’ businesses.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;The opportunity:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WPP is undergoing an exciting global transformation, and we&#39;re looking for a passionate and driven Backend Developer to join our dynamic and innovative team building Unite — a large-scale, cloud-native AI platform powering multiple WPP products. We encourage applications from a diverse range of backgrounds and experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you’ll be doing:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Backend Developer, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Design and build serverless microservices: Develop, deploy, and maintain AWS Lambda functions across a large TypeScript monorepo with 80+ backend services and 150+ shared packages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Own data and API layers: Design and implement REST APIs via API Gateway, work with DynamoDB and PostgreSQL (Aurora) for data storage, and integrate event-driven architectures using SQS and EventBridge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Scale AI-powered features: Contribute to backend services that orchestrate LLM-based agents, AI evaluation pipelines, and real-time content generation workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Collaborate and grow: Join a supportive and inclusive team focused on engineering best practices and continuous improvement. Share your knowledge and learn from others.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Gain business exposure: See the direct impact of your work and gain valuable business insights through regular interaction and feedback.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Contribute to technical excellence: Uphold high code-quality standards in a strict TypeScript codebase, write well-tested code with &amp;gt;85% coverage, and participate in code reviews.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Shape the future: Contribute your ideas and expertise to shape the future direction of our platform and development practices. We value diverse perspectives and encourage everyone to contribute to our ongoing innovation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
